## ForgeRoom Backend

This directory contains the backend and AI implementation for ForgeRoom.

### Services

- `forgeroom_backend.orchestrator.main:app`
  - FastAPI service on `:8000`
  - room lifecycle
  - supervisor processing
  - drift detection
  - AppSec agent
  - risk autopsy + export
- `forgeroom_backend.execution.main:app`
  - FastAPI service on `:8001`
  - diff generation
  - diff validation
  - git apply + commit
- `forgeroom_backend.websocket_gateway.main:app`
  - FastAPI/WebSocket service on `:8002`
  - realtime room chat
  - debounced orchestrator batching
  - vote broadcasting

### Layout

- `src/forgeroom_backend/shared`
  - shared contracts
  - SQLAlchemy models
  - repository helpers
  - export generation
  - demo repo bootstrap
- `src/forgeroom_backend/orchestrator`
  - AI provider abstraction
  - supervisor/drift/risk/AppSec nodes
- `src/forgeroom_backend/execution`
  - Gemini CLI wrapper
  - fallback diff generation
  - diff validation
  - git operations
- `src/forgeroom_backend/websocket_gateway`
  - connection manager
  - debounce buffer
  - websocket publishing

### Local Setup

From this directory:

```bash
pip install -e ".[test]"
```

Optional AI dependencies:

```bash
pip install -e ".[ai]"
```

### Run

```bash
uvicorn forgeroom_backend.orchestrator.main:app --reload --port 8000
uvicorn forgeroom_backend.execution.main:app --reload --port 8001
uvicorn forgeroom_backend.websocket_gateway.main:app --reload --port 8002
```

### Configuration

Environment variables use the `FORGEROOM_` prefix.

- `FORGEROOM_DATABASE_URL`
- `FORGEROOM_TARGET_REPO_PATH`
- `FORGEROOM_ORCHESTRATOR_URL`
- `FORGEROOM_ALLOW_GIT_PUSH`
- `FORGEROOM_ENABLE_DEMO_FALLBACKS`
- `FORGEROOM_GEMINI_API_KEY`
- `FORGEROOM_GEMINI_MODEL`

### Migrations

Alembic files live in `alembic/`.

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Tests

```bash
pytest tests -q
```
